  "title": "Microsoft Purview",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael and Sarah talk with guests Beau Faull&nbsp;\n                  (\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/beaufaull/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                  ) \n                  and Lou Mercuri&nbsp;\n                  (\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/lou-mercuri-4940b914/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                  ) \n\n                  about Microsoft Purview. Beau and Lou are also co-hosts of the <a target=\"_blank\" href='https://www.youtube.com/@coast2coast-msftau2'>Coast2Coast Podcast.</a>\n\n                  <br><br>\n                  We also discuss Azure Security news about Trusted Boot VMs, Sentinel and Defender for Cloud.\n\n                  <br><br>\n\n                  <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/824630?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/824630/\">Purview2</a></iframe>\n\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <!-- Links to news articles -->\n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/824630/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-pencil\"></i></a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/general-availability-trusted-launch-for-azure-vms-in-azure-for-us-government-regions/\">General availability: Trusted launch for Azure VMs in Azure for US Government regions</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/sentinel/whats-new\">What's new in Microsoft Sentinel</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/defender-for-cloud/how-to-manage-attack-path\">Identify and remediate attack paths</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/defender-for-cloud/how-to-manage-cloud-security-explorer\">Cloud security explorer</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-365/compliance/whats-new?view=o365-worldwide\">What's new in Microsoft Purview risk and compliance solutions</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-365/compliance/?view=o365-worldwide\">Microsoft Purview compliance documentation</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@coast2coast-msftau2\">Coast2Coast - MSFTAU</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/security/blog/2023/02/06/introducing-adaptive-protection-in-microsoft-purview-people-centric-data-protection-for-a-multiplatform-world/\">Introducing Adaptive Protection in Microsoft Purview—People-centric data protection for a multiplatform world</a></li>\n                  </ul>"
